# Interdisciplinary Science Rankings Survey 2026 now open-- AGH UST 

URL: https://agh.edu.pl/en/employees/news/detail/interdisciplinary-science-rankings-survey-2026-now-open
Crawled: 2025-03-19 21:22:32

Interdisciplinary Science Rankings Survey 2026 now open 

 17-02-2025 

 We highly encourage all interested academics to participate in THE's Interdisciplinary Science Research Survey conducted for the purpose of the Times Higher Education Interdisciplinary Science Rankings. 

It will take around 
5 minutes 
to complete the survey. 

The survey will close on 
31 May 2025.
